Baseline urbanization level among quartiles of daily average concentration of air pollutants
* Chi-square test. The urbanization level was categorized by the population density of the residential area into
4 levels, with level 1 as the most urbanized and level 4 as the least urbanized. The daily average air pollutant
concentrations were categorized into 4 groups based on quartiles for each air pollutant.
